HEADWORD: Undecide
<hw>Un`de*cide"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>decide</ets>.]</ety> <def>To reverse or recant, as
a previous decision.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

